A Drupal module with some node addons. Theses include the following:

Referenced User Node permission
-------------------------------
Allow's user referenced in nodes via the CCK User reference field to have the same permission over the node as the node creator

Please choose the correct permission, you won't have access to node publish tools if you don't choose correct permissions.

Quick Links
-----------
Allow admin links on nodes for easy access

This module is still very much in development, so use with caution.